    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115290/extras/bcfefdbfaf01df14a8ba71b30ef299ff.avif?t=1747068500\" width=600 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tears of Vanfell - Chapter 1 是一款充满动作元素的地下城探索游戏，包含类roguelike (肉鸽游戏) 和砍杀元素。在众多角色之间进行选择，在在线合作模式中，您可以交换武器并作为最多四人的团队爬上山峰，不断壮大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115290/extras/570ccb14e3f4762bc5d420c17b62de2f.avif?t=1747068500\" width=600 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索并爬上程序生成的山峰，寻找并击败 Boss，然后继续您的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115290/extras/e84ee4b71e87d6ff953ad5683d3a9b48.avif?t=1747068500\" width=600 height=248 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在冒险过程中，您将获得强大的新能力、武器和装备，如果您打算生存，就需要使用所有这些能力、武器和装备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115290/extras/b2256537e8fd48106f2fd9ea453d6b74.avif?t=1747068500\" width=600 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115290/extras/b85b5b9a56d201452b8745b08b369983.avif?t=1747068500\" width=600 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与最多四人的团队一起探索山峰！或者，如果您宁愿独自征服山峰，也不要担心 - 您也可以带上营地的另一名成员来帮助您。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115290/extras/d06c724441f879ab85fe6dfcbcfcd756.avif?t=1747068500\" width=600 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在您的营地为下一次探险做好准备。起初，只有您和您的想法......但随着您的探索，您会发现其他人愿意帮助您 - 从具有独特技能的其他探险家到可以在幕后提供帮助的专家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115290/extras/40241a0136463eae5121fe8404afe9a6.avif?t=1747068500\" width=600 height=259 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115290/extras/20ac5b0f7e5b15243726945712644131.avif?t=1747068500\" width=600 height=226 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在冒险过程中，您会遇到许多角色，并逐渐了解他们和他们的动机。但您也可能会发现自己陷入了百年战争的余波中…… </p>",
